---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
HOW TO
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

to run tests from "prod" environment use the command (tests will be executed in chrome by default) - mvn clean test "-Dcucumber.options=--tags @smoke" -DConfig=prod

to run tests from "prod" environment in firefox - mvn clean test "-Dcucumber.options=--tags @smoke" -DConfig=prod -Dselenide.browser=firefox